{"type":"message","id":"d2677cef","parentId":"f4a6e536","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:27:51.083Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:5f09e72e-67ca-4669-b0cd-2a072f3a882b 广西换电充电日报资讯] 请从百度、360、必应、微信搜狗等搜索引擎搜索并整理关于广西区内换电业务、两轮低速充电业务的最新资讯。\n\n搜索关键词：\n- 广西换电站建设运营\n- 广西两轮电动车充电设施\n- 铁塔能源广西业务\n- 广西充换电政策法规\n- 广西充电设施招标\n\n内容涵盖：\n1. 广西换电业务动态\n2. 广西充电业务动态\n3. 政府政策法规\n4. 行业标准发布\n5. 招投标信息\n6. 行业合作动态\n\n请按以下格式整理成美观的简报：\n\n📰 广西换电充电日报资讯 - [日期]\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n🔥 今日热点\n[列出2-3条最重要的新闻，每条包含标题、摘要、来源链接]\n\n📋 政策动态\n[政府政策、法规文件、补贴政策等]\n\n💼 行业动态\n[行业新闻、企业动态、市场趋势等]\n\n📢 招投标信息\n[相关招标、中标信息]\n\n🤝 行业合作\n[企业合作、战略合作等动态]\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n💡 营销建议\n[基于今日资讯，针对铁塔能源换电及充电业务提出2-3条营销建议]\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n📌 数据来源：百度、360、必应、微信搜狗\n\n每条新闻需包含：标题、摘要（2-3句话）、原文链接、发布时间。\n\n通过微信发送给用户，格式美观，重点突出。\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 22nd, 2026 — 9:27 AM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-22 01:27 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774142871082}}
{"type":"message","id":"87c0fab7","parentId":"d2677cef","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:27:56.839Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户需要我搜索关于广西换电业务和两轮低速充电业务的最新资讯，然后整理成日报格式。让我先读取multi-search-engine skill来了解如何进行多搜索引擎搜索。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jduwj83yp6xz_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Applications/QClaw.app/Contents/Resources/openclaw/config/skills/multi-search-engine/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qclaw","model":"modelroute","usage":{"input":18065,"output":127,"cacheRead":1533,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19725,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774142871083}}
{"type":"message","id":"0cc94021","parentId":"87c0fab7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T01:27:57.157Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_jduwj83yp6xz_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: \"multi-search-engine\"\ndescription: 多搜索引擎聚合，集成 17 个引擎（8 个国内 + 9 个国际）。支持高级搜索语法、时间筛选、站内搜索、隐私引擎和 WolframAlpha 知识查询。无需 API 密钥。\n---\n\n# Multi Search Engine v2.0.1\n\nIntegration of 17 search engines for web crawling without API keys.\n\n## Search Engines\n\n### Domestic (8)\n- **Baidu**: `https://www.baidu.com/s?wd={keyword}`\n- **Bing CN**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=0`\n- **Bing INT**: `https://cn.bing.com/search?q={keyword}&ensearch=1`\n- **360**: `https://www.so.com/s?q={keyword}`\n- **Sogou**: `https://sogou.com/web?query={keyword}`\n- **WeChat**: `https://wx.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&query={keyword}`\n- **Toutiao**: `https://so.toutiao.com/search?keyword={keyword}`\n- **Jisilu**: `https://www.jisilu.cn/explore/?keyword={keyword}`\n\n### International (9)\n- **Google**: `https://www.google.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Google HK**: `https://www.google.com.hk/search?q={keyword}`\n- **DuckDuckGo**: `https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q={keyword}`\n- **Yahoo**: `https://search.yahoo.com/search?p={keyword}`\n- **Startpage**: `https://www.startpage.com/sp/search?query={keyword}`\n- **Brave**: `https://search.brave.com/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Ecosia**: `https://www.ecosia.org/search?q={keyword}`\n- **Qwant**: `https://www.qwant.com/?q={keyword}`\n- **WolframAlpha**: `https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i={keyword}`\n\n## Quick Examples\n\n```javascript\n// Basic search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=python+tutorial\"})\n\n// Site-specific\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=site:github.com+react\"})\n\n// File type\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=machine+learning+filetype:pdf\"})\n\n// Time filter (past week)\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.google.com/search?q=ai+news&tbs=qdr:w\"})\n\n// Privacy search\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=privacy+tools\"})\n\n// DuckDuckGo Bangs\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://duckduckgo.com/html/?q=!gh+tensorflow\"})\n\n// Knowledge calculation\nweb_fetch({\"url\": \"https://www.wolframalpha.com/input?i=100+USD+to+CNY\"})\n```\n\n## Advanced Operators\n\n| Operator | Example | Description |\n|----------|---------|-------------|\n| `site:` | `site:github.com python` | Search within site |\n| `filetype:` | `filetype:pdf report` | Specific file type |\n| `\"\"` | `\"machine learning\"` | Exact match |\n| `-` | `python -snake` | Exclude term |\n| `OR` | `cat OR dog` | Either term |\n\n## Time Filters\n\n| Parameter | Description |\n|-----------|-------------|\n| `tbs=qdr:h` | Past hour |\n| `tbs=qdr:d` | Past day |\n| `tbs=qdr:w` | Past week |\n| `tbs=qdr:m` | Past month |\n| `tbs=qdr:y` | Past year |\n\n## Privacy Engines\n\n- **DuckDuckGo**: No tracking\n- **Startpage**: Google results + privacy\n- **Brave**: Independent index\n- **Qwant**: EU GDPR compliant\n\n## Bangs Shortcuts (DuckDuckGo)\n\n| Bang | Destination |\n|------|-------------|\n| `!g` | Google |\n| `!gh` | GitHub |\n| `!so` | Stack Overflow |\n| `!w` | Wikipedia |\n| `!yt` | YouTube |\n\n## WolframAlpha Queries\n\n- Math: `integrate x^2 dx`\n- Conversion: `100 USD to CNY`\n- Stocks: `AAPL stock`\n- Weather: `weather in Beijing`\n\n## Documentation\n\n- `references/advanced-search.md` - Domestic search guide\n- `references/international-search.md` - International search guide\n- `CHANGELOG.md` - Version history\n\n## License\n\nMIT\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774142877154}}
